name: Experiment Or Die #41
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. This  space has got my brain moving a million miles an hour all the time. I'm more motivated than ever, more inspired, more anxious and more unsure of what is coming than ever before. It makes me incredibly happy and nervous at the same time and #41 is me trying to personify the totality of how I feel right now! Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
